  <brief_title>Use Of Capnography As Surrogate Measure Of PC02 In Medical Intensive Care Unit (ICU) Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use Of Capnography As Surrogate Measure Of PC02 In Medical ICU Patients</official_title>
